title: I Can Be Your Girl Trend 12/09: Louis Tomlinson, Cyberpunk 2077, Real Madrid, Nigella Lawson
itunes:title: I Can Be Your Girl Trend 12/09: Louis Tomlinson, Cyberpunk 2077, Real Madrid, Nigella Lawson
description:
On this edition of I Can Be Your Girl Trend Miles and DJ Danl discuss Louis Tomlinson of One D putting out a video with long hair (ahh!!!), conversations around the working conditions at CD Projekt Red arise again now that Cyberpunk is out, Real Madrid is not looking so good since Ronaldo left, and Nigella Lawson mispronounces "Microwave" for a laugh and everyone took it way too seriously.
